    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents beautifully inside and out. It runs and drives exactly as it should, appears extremely well cared for, and shows only the slightest signs of age or use. The interior is clean and well-kept, the exterior retains an excellent appearance, and overall it feels like a properly maintained, high-quality car. A buyer can expect a standout vehicle that needs nothing beyond normal ownership and enjoyment.",
