    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Runs and drives, but this is a fair-condition car with clear signs of age and use. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, including blemishes, scuffs, and general wear consistent with a vehicle that has been driven and not restored. It is a usable driver as-is, but a buyer should plan on some maintenance, repairs, or reconditioning depending on how nice they want it to be. Good fit for someone looking for an affordable entry point and willing to put in a little work over time.",
      "price": 18900.0,
