      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left to give? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy runabout, or a project to make their own. It has honest wear consistent with age, but it still offers real value at a price that keeps things sensible. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and full of potential, this could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project-platform with solid enthusiast appeal. The powertrain fires up and the car offers a good mechanical foundation for someone wanting an affordable driver/project with upgrade potential. Chassis and running gear feel like a workable base, and it presents as an honest vehicle for someone who values function over cosmetics. Not perfect and priced accordingly, but a compelling opportunity to get into a capable platform without spending premium money.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Rough around the edges, priced to move, and ready for someone who just needs basic wheels.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with character, this ride has the kind of well-worn charm that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who appreciates a vehicle with stories to tell and plenty of potential left to give\u2014whether you need an affordable daily driver, a practical backup, or a fun project to make your own. If you love machines with personality instead of cookie-cutter sameness, this one brings a spirited presence that\u2019s hard to fake.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
